4. Expert Accuracy Requirements
Primary Success Metric
Expert accuracy is the MAIN aspect of this project. Each expert must meet minimum precision and recall thresholds on a manually annotated gold standard test set.
- Gold standard: 200 manually annotated edges per expert type
- Evaluation: Precision, Recall, F1-score on held-out test set
- Threshold: All experts must achieve minimum F1 to pass

4.1 Expert Performance Targets
Expert	Precision	Recall	F1 Min	F1 Target	Priority
Cross-Reference Hunter	>= 85%	>= 80%	82%	88%	P0
Causal Chain Builder	>= 75%	>= 70%	72%	78%	P0
Temporal Linker	>= 90%	>= 85%	87%	92%	P1
Table-Text Connector	>= 85%	>= 75%	80%	85%	P1
